{
  "texts": [
    "Emerging LLM solutions suggest a future where these models serve as autonomous teaching assistants, dynamically adjusting curriculum materials to suit class mastery levels.",
    "The convergence of LLMs with augmented and virtual reality can create immersive grading environments, offer instant feedback, and enhance understanding of complex topics 42.",
    "The Future of grading with LLMs.",
    "An essential transformation in LLM-integrated grading is the transition from summative to formative assessment.",
    "Instead of merely assigning scores, LLMs focus on understanding the process of knowledge acquisition and the development of critical thinking skills, thus contributing to a more nuanced view of student learning progression."
  ]
}